questions.question: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI-Remover node?
questions.answer: The ComfyUI-Remover node makes parts of the image transparent.

questions.question: What parts of the image can be removed using the ComfyUI-Remover node?
questions.answer: Currently, the node can remove the background and face from an image.

questions.question: Where can I find an example of the ComfyUI-Remover node in action?
questions.answer: An example image is provided at the end of the documentation.

questions.question: What are the limitations of the ComfyUI-Remover node?
questions.answer: The node is still in progress and does not support the removal of other parts of the image.
